"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel has launched new attacks on Tehran. There was an explosion near a rally in the city. The US Central Command is working on rescue efforts after a refueling aircraft crashed in western Iraq.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Attacks Tehran\",            \"translated_version\": \"Israel ha lanzado nuevos ataques en Teher\u00e1n. Hubo una explosi\u00f3n cerca de una reuni\u00f3n en la ciudad. El Comando Central de EE.UU. est\u00e1 trabajando en rescates despu\u00e9s de que un avi\u00f3n se estrell\u00f3 en el oeste de Irak.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Israel Ataca Teher\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Indigenous leaders told Charles about the threat from a movement during a meeting in London.\",            \"english_title\": \"Indigenous Leaders Warn Charles\",            \"translated_version\": \"L\u00edderes ind\u00edgenas le dijeron a Charles sobre la amenaza de un movimiento durante una reuni\u00f3n en Londres.\",            \"translated_title\": \"L\u00edderes Ind\u00edgenas Advierten a Charles\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Drones, cruise missiles, and fighter jets are often seen by sailors stuck on ships in the Gulf. Some sailors died when an Iranian warship was sunk by a US submarine near Sri Lanka.\",            \"english_title\": \"Sailors See Drones and Jets\",            \"translated_version\": \"Drones, misiles y aviones de combate son vistos por marineros en barcos en el Golfo. Algunos marineros murieron cuando un barco de guerra iran\u00ed fue hundido por un submarino de EE.UU. cerca de Sri Lanka.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Marineros Ven Drones y Aviones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The biggest election contest is for the mayor of Paris, which has been controlled by the left for 25 years.\",            \"english_title\": \"Paris Mayor Election\",            \"translated_version\": \"La elecci\u00f3n m\u00e1s grande es para el alcalde de Par\u00eds, que ha sido controlado por la izquierda por 25 a\u00f1os.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Elecci\u00f3n de Alcalde de Par\u00eds\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The FBI is looking into an incident as a targeted act of violence against the Jewish community.\",            \"english_title\": \"FBI Investigates Violence\",            \"translated_version\": \"El FBI est\u00e1 investigando un incidente como un acto de violencia contra la comunidad jud\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"FBI Investiga Violencia\"        }    ]}"